"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459296","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2016-03-18","<p>The appointment panel satisfied itself there were no conflicts of interest when they made recommendations to Ministers. In due course and as is usual practice, the Adjudicator’s office will publish a register of interests.</p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry",,"2016-03-18T14:11:30.4Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459296/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459296/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459296/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2016-03-10","Pubs Code Adjudicator","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, if he will publish the actual or potential conflicts of interest declared by the Pubs Code Adjudicator, Mr Paul Newby, prior to his appointment.","false","Biography information for Greg Mulholland","Leeds North West","Greg Mulholland","30688"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459297","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2016-03-18","<p>It is standard Government practice not to provide such information. The Government only provides such information about the successful candidate.</p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry",,"2016-03-18T14:08:01.53Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459297/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459297/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459297/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2016-03-10","Pubs Code Adjudicator","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, how many applicants to the Pubs Code Adjudicator role declared actual or potential conflicts of interest.","false","Biography information for Greg Mulholland","Leeds North West","Greg Mulholland","30689"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459298","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2016-03-18","<p>As is standard practice, Mr Newby was asked during the appointments process to declare any potential conflicts of interest.</p>","Broxtowe","Anna Soubry",,"2016-03-18T14:02:28.82Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459298/answer","Biography information for Anna Soubry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459298/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/459298/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2016-03-10","Pubs Code Adjudicator","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, what discussions his Department or its employment agency adviser had with Mr Paul Newby about actual and potential conflicts of interest prior to his appointment as the Pubs Code Adjudicator.","false","Biography information for Greg Mulholland","Leeds North West","Greg Mulholland","30690"
